emic background and career goals\r\n•	Securing a Letter of Acceptance (LOA) from partner universities and colleges\r\n•	Preparation of financial documents required for visa applications\r\n•	Obtaining the Form I-20 for USA student visas\r\n•	Obtaining the Provincial Attestation Letter (PAL) for Canada study permit applications\r\n•	Visa application assistance through licensed immigration expert partners, including trusted professionals such as BorderPass in Canada\r\n•	Scholarship guidance to help students identify funding opportunities\r\n•	Educational consultancy and admission support for international universities\r\n•	Assistance with Permanent Residence (PR) applications through our partner BorderPass (this is an additional service and not our main mission)\r\n•	Assistance in job seeking opportunities for graduates and professionals (this is an additional support service and not our primary mission)\r\nOur goal is to provide professional guidance from school selection to visa application, helping students successfully begin their international education and move abroad journey.','[0.026347533,0.009379584,0.057776865,0.01255571,-0.039624307,-0.0062377956,0.01545142,0.01588635,-0.012578601,0.033787105,0.043698907,0.0018942297,-0.0033706988,-0.020006727,-0.055670895,0.0467663,0.07773781,0.04305796,-0.013414122,0.0635454,0.047521703,0.034862984,-0.049261417,-0.0033249168,0.007365177,-0.004475189,0.017751966,0.03687739,0.0027540727,-0.027812557,0.02861374,0.0023162824,-0.043469995,0.0016796266,-0.007130544,0.011685852,0.023669288,-0.03804483,-0.02950649,-0.018129667,0.020567557,0.04589644,0.046171132,-0.0039057757,-0.0044007935,0.050634876,-0.0249054,-0.0070962077,-0.037655685,0.018541705,-0.074533075,0.060706913,0.016149595,0.050039712,-0.02251329,-0.036373787,0.047109663,-0.033123266,-0.018015211,0.016080923,0.050818004,0.0044465754,0.0050646323,0.033466633,0.0027941319,0.055258855,-0.038411085,0.042989284,-0.05878407,0.016641751,0.014329761,0.059104543,0.003236214