0.013508177,-0.009782955,0.018999767,-0.0017918433,0.014108289,-0.02672196,-0.034738548,-0.0071956804,0.014685755,0.009748986,0.018875215]',1,'2026-03-15 03:27:28','2026-03-15 03:27:29','faq',0,NULL),(10,1,'What documents are required for a study visa?','The required documents for a study visa application may vary depending on the destination country, university requirements, and visa type. However, most applicants are typically required to provide the following documents:\r\nFor Bachelor’s Degree Applicants\r\n•	High School Diploma\r\n•	High School Academic Reports / Transcripts\r\n•	Valid Passport\r\n•	English Language Certificate (IELTS, TOEFL, or equivalent if required)\r\n•	Medium of Instruction (MOI) Certificate\r\n•	Personal Statement / Statement of Purpose\r\n•	Updated Curriculum Vitae (CV) (sometimes required)\r\n•	Recommendation Letters (depending on the university)\r\nFor Master’s Degree Applicants\r\n•	Bachelor’s Degree Certificate\r\n•	Bachelor’s Academic Transcripts\r\n•	Valid Passport\r\n•	English Language Certificate or MOI\r\n•	Personal Statement\r\n•	Updated CV\r\n•	Two Recommendation Letters\r\nFor PhD Applicants\r\n•	Master’s Degree Certificate\r\n•	Master’s Academic Transcripts\r\n•	Research Proposal (for some programs)\r\n•	Updated CV\r\n•	Recommendation Letters\r\n•	English Language Certificate or MOI\r\nOther Important Documents\r\n•	Letter of Acceptance (LOA) from the university\r\n•	Financial documents or proof of funds\r\nWhat is a Medium of Instruction (MOI)?\r\nA Medium of Instruction (MOI) is an official certificate issued by the university or school where you previously studied. It confirms that your previous education was taught in English and that you are capable of continuing your studies in English.\r\nMany universities—especially our partner universities in Europe, Turkey, North Cyprus, and some other countries—accept MOI as proof of English proficiency, meaning students may not need to take an English test such as IELTS or TOEFL.\r\nHowever, MOI acceptance depends on the university and the destination country, so our team guides applicants on whether MOI will be accepted or if an English test is required.\r\nKeywords:\r\nstudy visa requirements, student visa documents, Medium of Instruction MOI, English proficiency proof, study abroad admission documents, bachelor admission requirements, masters admission requirements, PhD admission documents.','[-0.01168060302734375,0.0484619140625,0.04425048828125,-0.019622802734375,-0.0136566162109375,-0.0124969482421875,0.0513916015625,-0.005100250244140625,-0.007350921630859375,0.0311431884765625,-0.01024627685546875,-0.01474761962890625,-0.0210113525390625,-0.02911376953125,-0.0224456787109375,0.07440185546875,0.0185394287109375,0.0171051025390625,-0.0031337738037109375,0.0032291412353515625,0.05511474609375,0.0282440185546875,-0.01153564453125,-0.0038394927978515625,0.044342041015625,-0.046295166015625,0.028900146484375,0.004093170166015625,0.018951416015625,-0.031982421875,0.0467529296875,-0.019775390625,0.007518768310546875,0.0092620849609375,-0.039459228515625,0.03729248046875,0.01070404052734375,-0.021453857421875,0.0043792724609375,-0.052734375,-0.045501708984375,0.02203369140625,0.01477813720703125,-0.028289794921875,-0.051239013671875,0.0074310302734375,0.01422119140625,-0.010986328125,0.01325225830078125,0.01373291015625,-0.019805908203125,-0.005321502685546875,0.019256591796875,0.05194091796875,0.0173187255859375,-0.03985595703125,0.037017822265625,-0.052581787109375,-0.042266845703125,-0.0297088623046875,0.0102081298828125,0.0244293212890625,0.005649566650390625,-0.01275634765625,0.01995849609375,0.0021228790283203125,0.0133819580078125,0.018585205078125,-0.052764892578125,0.0173797607421875,0.0638427734375,0.0252685546875,0.022674560546875,-0.0093231201171875,-0.0228424072265625,0.0212554931640625,-0.03240966796875,0.017578125,0.00428009033203125,0.0232086181640625,-0.05340576171875,0.0178985595703125,0.0252838134765625,-0.0227508544921875