26-03-15 04:39:08','2026-03-15 04:39:09','faq',0,NULL),(12,1,'What is Parrot Canada Visa Consultant Co. Ltd?','Parrot Canada Visa Consultant Co. Ltd is an international education and visa consultancy company that assists students and professionals with study abroad programs, visa applications, scholarships, and educational opportunities worldwide.\r\nOur team provides comprehensive guidance throughout the entire study abroad process, including:\r\n•	School and program selection based on the student’s academic background and    career goals\r\n•	Securing a Letter of Acceptance (LOA) from partner universities and colleges\r\n•	Preparation of financial documents required for visa applications\r\n•	Obtaining the Form I-20 for USA student visas\r\n•	Obtaining the Provincial Attestation Letter (PAL) for Canada study permits\r\n•	Visa application assistance through licensed immigration expert partners, including trusted professionals such as BorderPass in Canada\r\n•	Assistance with Permanent Residence (PR) applications through our partner BorderPass (this is an additional service and not our main mission)\r\n•	Assistance in job seeking opportunities for graduates and professionals (this is an additional support service and not our primary mission)\r\nFrom the initial consultation to the final visa decision, Parrot Canada Visa Consultant Co. Ltd ensures that students receive professional guidance to successfully begin their international education and move abroad journey.','[0.0311279296875,0.01300048828125,0.042266845703125,0.032928466796875,-0.037750244140625,-0.0042572021484375,0.01142120361328125,0.0192108154296875,-0.021484375,0.01496124267578125,0.03814697265625,0.0020160675048828125,-0.0151519775390625,-0.019927978515625,-0.05291748046875,0.051422119140625,0.06658935546875,0.0248565673828125,-0.014495849609375,0.05633544921875,0.045196533203125,0.02899169921875,-0.05462646484375,0.003978729248046875,-0.001476287841796875,-0.004558563232421875,0.0164947509765625,0.05