,NULL,NULL,NULL),(31,4,'outgoing','text','That\'s great to hear that you want to study in South Korea! We have a presence in South Korea with an office located in Gasan-dong, Geumcheon-gu, Seoul, Republic of Korea. Our team there can assist you with choosing the right university, understanding the admission process, and guiding you through the student visa application.\n\nPlease feel free to contact our South Korea representative at +82 10-9632-1984 for in-person consultation or any questions you may have about studying in South Korea. We can also help you prepare for your visa interview and ensure you have all the necessary documentation.\n\nWould you like me to provide you with more detailed information about universities, courses, or the visa process for studying in South Korea?',NULL,NULL,NULL,'read',0,0,NULL,'2026-03-02 23:05:13','2026-03-02 23:05:16','\"{\\\"confidence\\\":0.65,\\\"source\\\":\\\"grounded_ai\\\"}\"','wamid.HBgMMjU0NzExODA3NjQ2FQIAERgSODA4M0EzRjUyNjVGQUFCMjZGAA==',NULL,NULL),(32,4,'incoming','text','Need also to study in usa',NULL,NULL,NULL,'received',1,1,'2026-03-04 02:47:16','2026-03-02 23:25:41','2026-03-04 02:47:16',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(33,4,'outgoing','text','The USA is one of our key focus areas. Our global education and immigration expertise covers the USA, and we can guide you through the process of selecting the right university, applying for your student visa (F-1), and preparing for your life as an international student in America. below is fees structure for USA',NULL,NULL,NULL,'delivered',0,0,NULL,'2026-03-02 23:25:42','2026-03-02 23:25:47','\"{\\\"confidence\\\":0.6074208838291458,\\\"source\\\":\\\"faq_semantic\\\"}\"','wamid.HBgMMjU0NzExODA3NjQ2FQIAERgSNzgzOEU4MUY0N0I2RTdCODU2AA==',NULL,NULL),(34,4,'outgoing','text','[Attachment]',NULL,NULL,NULL,'read',0,0,NULL,'2026-03-02 23:25:42','2026-03-02 23:25:45','\"{\\\"type\\\":\\\"document\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https:\\\\\\/\\\\\\/parrotcanada.site\\\\\\/storage\\\\\\/faq_attachments\\