tion, cultural adaptation, and travel tips.\n7. **Post-Arrival Support:** We help you settle in Canada, including guidance on opening bank accounts, getting health insurance, and adapting to your new environment.\n\nFor detailed help with university admissions and student pathways, please contact our dedicated admissions team at:  \n**admission@visaconsultantcanada.com**\n\nFeel free to ask if you need information about specific universities, programs, or detailed steps to start your study journey in Canada!',NULL,NULL,NULL,'read',0,0,NULL,'2026-03-04 03:20:38','2026-03-04 03:27:10','\"{\\\"confidence\\\":0.65,\\\"source\\\":\\\"grounded_ai\\\"}\"','wamid.HBgMMjU0NzExODA3NjQ2FQIAERgSQTE5RUZDMEU5MTRBOTI0QjgxAA==',NULL,NULL),(49,4,'incoming','text','Hello',NULL,NULL,NULL,'received',0,1,NULL,'2026-03-04 05:01:47','2026-03-04 05:05:04',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(50,4,'outgoing','text','Hello 👋 How can we assist you?',NULL,NULL,NULL,'read',0,0,NULL,'2026-03-04 05:01:47','2026-03-04 05:01:50','\"{\\\"confidence\\\":1,\\\"source\\\":\\\"system\\\"}\"','wamid.HBgMMjU0NzExODA3NjQ2FQIAERgSNjNGOUIyRTExRUI2QTczNzM1AA==',NULL,NULL),(51,4,'incoming','text','Hello',NULL,NULL,NULL,'received',0,1,NULL,'2026-03-04 06:02:47','2026-03-04 06:05:05',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(52,4,'outgoing','text','Hello 👋 How can we assist you?',NULL,NULL,NULL,'read',0,0,NULL,'2026-03-04 06:02:47','2026-03-04 06:02:49','\"{\\\"confidence\\\":1,\\\"source\\\":\\\"system\\\"}\"','wamid.HBgMMjU0NzExODA3NjQ2FQIAERgSRDgxQkM3QTBFQ0QwQ0VBRjk5AA==',NULL,NULL),(53,4,'incoming','text','Need to study in usa',NULL,NULL,NULL,'received',0,1,NULL,'2026-03-04 06:03:30','2026-03-04 06:05:05',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(54,4,'outgoing','text','The USA is one of our key focus areas. Our global education and immigration expertise covers the USA, and we can guide you through the process of selecting the right university, applying for your student visa (F-1), and preparing for your life as an international student in America. below is fees