NDJDQkEyOTQxRTEyM0IyAA==',NULL,NULL),(85,1,'incoming','text','Need to study in canada',NULL,NULL,NULL,'received',0,1,NULL,'2026-03-06 12:13:31','2026-03-06 12:15:04',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(86,1,'outgoing','text','Great! I can help you with that. To study in Canada, you\'ll generally need to apply for a Study Permit. Here’s a step-by-step overview of what you need to do:\n\n1. **Choose a Program and School**  \n   Find a Designated Learning Institution (DLI) in Canada that offers the program you want to study.\n\n2. **Apply and Get an Acceptance Letter**  \n   Apply to the school and receive an official acceptance letter. This letter is required for your study permit application.\n\n3. **Check Eligibility Requirements**  \n   Make sure you meet the eligibility criteria, such as:  \n   - Proof of acceptance from a DLI  \n   - Proof of sufficient funds to support yourself and pay for tuition  \n   - No criminal record (if required)  \n   - Good health (you may need a medical exam)  \n   - Intent to leave Canada after your studies or comply with permit conditions\n\n4. **Gather Required Documents**  \n   Common documents include:  \n   - Acceptance letter  \n   - Valid passport or travel document  \n   - Proof of financial support  \n   - Passport-sized photos  \n   - Letter of explanation  \n   - Immigration medical exam report (if applicable)  \n   - Police clearance certificate (if applicable)\n\n5. **Apply for a Study Permit**  \n   You can apply online or at a Visa Application Center. Include all required documents and pay the application fee.\n\n6. **Biometrics and Interview**  \n   Depending on your country, you might need to provide biometrics (fingerprints and photo) and/or attend an interview.\n\n7. **Wait for Processing**  \n   Processing times vary by country.\n\n8. **Prepare for Arrival**  \n   Once approved, you’ll get a Port of Entry Letter of Introduction. Make sure to bring this and all your documents when you travel.\n\n---\n\nIf you want, I can help you find DLI institutions, prepare your documents, or guide you through the application form. Just let me know!',NULL,NULL,NULL,'delivered',0,0,NULL,'2026-03-06 12:13:46','2026-03-06 12:13:50','\"{\\\"confidence\\\":0.5,\\\"source\\\":\\\"ai\\\"}\"','wamid.HBgMMjU0NzExODA3NjQ2FQIAERgSMDI1MEVFRjUxRkU0OTZFMjQ2AA==',NULL,NULL),(87,1,'incoming','text','Hello',NULL,NULL,NULL,'received',0,1,NULL,'2026-03-06 16:29:04','2026-03-06 16:30:05',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(88,1,'outgoing','text','Hello 👋 How can we assist you?',NULL,NULL,NULL,'read',0,0,NULL,'2026-03-06 16:29:04','2026-03-06 16:29:07','\"{\\\"confidence\\\":1,\\\"source\\\":\\\"system\\\"}\"','wamid.HBgMMjU0NzExODA3NjQ2FQIAERgSNUI3QUI0RTI3QkQ3RUIzMTY1AA==',NULL,NULL),(89,1,'incoming','text','Want to go in iran',NULL,NULL,NULL,'received',0,1,NULL,'2026-03-06 16:29:21','2026-03-06 16:30:05',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(90,1,'outgoing','text','Sure! I can help you with that. To assist you better, could you please provide me with the following details?\n\n1. Your nationality/citizenship  \n2. The purpose of your visit (tourism, business, study, etc.)  \n3. The intended duration of your stay in Iran  \n4. Your current location (country) where you will apply for the visa  \n\nWith this information, I can provide you with the specific visa requirements and application process for Iran.',NULL,NULL,NULL,'read',0,0,NULL,'2026-03-06 16:29:28','2026-03-06 16:35:28','\"{\\\"confidence\\\":0.5,\\\"source\\\":\\\"ai\\\"}\"','wamid.HBgMMjU0NzExODA3NjQ2FQIAERgSOURFNUE5Q0QyNzMzRjFGRjY5AA==',NULL,NULL),(91,1,'incoming','text','Hello',NULL,NULL,NULL,'received',0,1,NULL,'2026-03-07 04:02:51','2026-03-07 04:05:04',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(92,1,'outgoing','text','Hello 👋 How can we assist you?',NULL,NULL,NULL,'read',0,0,NULL,'2026-03-07 04:02:51','2026-03-07 04:04:15','\"{\\\"confidence\\\":1,\\\"source\\\":\\\"system\\\"}\"','wamid.HBgMMjU0NzExODA3NjQ2FQIAERgSQTY4MTQyMTAzNzFCOEZDODBEAA==',NULL,NULL),(93,1,'incoming','text','Want to study in usa',NULL,