xt','Hello!\n\nIf you are interested in moving to Canada, Parrot Canada can help you with a variety of services including:\n\n- Initial eligibility assessment to understand your options\n- Assistance with university and program selection if you want to study\n- Help with student visa or study permit applications\n- Guidance on work visa pathways if you want to work in Canada\n- Consulting for permanent residence applications\n- Pre-departure briefings and post-arrival settlement support\n\nPlease let us know your specific goals (studying, working, immigrating) and any questions you have, so we can tailor our advice accordingly.\n\nYou can contact us anytime by email at: infos@visaconsultantcanada.com. We’ll be happy to connect you with the right consultant and guide you through the process.\n\nLooking forward to assisting you with your Canada plans!',NULL,NULL,NULL,'sent',0,0,NULL,'2026-03-07 05:27:28','2026-03-07 05:27:31','\"{\\\"confidence\\\":0.65,\\\"source\\\":\\\"grounded_ai\\\"}\"','wamid.HBgLMTQzODI5MDY2ODgVAgARGBI5MTJERjJGRDVDODc0RjlDMEMA',NULL,NULL),(112,3,'incoming','text','what is next',NULL,NULL,NULL,'received',0,1,NULL,'2026-03-07 05:43:01','2026-03-07 05:45:04',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(113,3,'outgoing','text','Could you please provide more details about your situation? For example, have you already submitted a visa application, completed an interview, or received any communication from the visa office? This information will help me guide you on the next steps.',NULL,NULL,NULL,'read',0,0,NULL,'2026-03-07 05:43:05','2026-03-07 05:43:27','\"{\\\"confidence\\\":0.5,\\\"source\\\":\\\"ai\\\"}\"','wamid.HBgLMTQzODI5MDY2ODgVAgARGBI4MjM1NTZFMzA5M0Y5MEQ5QUEA',NULL,NULL),(114,1,'incoming','text','Hello',NULL,NULL,NULL,'received',0,1,NULL,'2026-03-07 05:58:04','2026-03-07 06:00:05',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(115,1,'outgoing','text','Hello 👋 How can we assist you?',NULL,NULL,NULL,'delivered',0,0,NULL,'2026-03-07 05:58:04','2026-03-07 05:58:07','\"{\\\"confidence\\\":1,\