ed',0,0,NULL,'2026-03-07 08:36:36','2026-03-07 08:36:39','\"{\\\"confidence\\\":1,\\\"source\\\":\\\"system_onboarding\\\"}\"','wamid.HBgMOTcxNTQyMTk0NTc2FQIAERgSODE3NjdBQkIwOEY1NDVDNDUyAA==',NULL,NULL),(169,5,'incoming','text','idieudonne622@gmail.com',NULL,NULL,NULL,'received',0,1,NULL,'2026-03-07 08:37:08','2026-03-07 08:40:05',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(170,5,'outgoing','text','✅ Thank you! You can now ask your questions.',NULL,NULL,NULL,'delivered',0,0,NULL,'2026-03-07 08:37:08','2026-03-07 08:37:11','\"{\\\"confidence\\\":1,\\\"source\\\":\\\"system_onboarding\\\"}\"','wamid.HBgMOTcxNTQyMTk0NTc2FQIAERgSOENEOEE4REUxRjE2ODlGOENCAA==',NULL,NULL),(171,5,'incoming','text','I want Canada visa',NULL,NULL,NULL,'received',0,1,NULL,'2026-03-07 08:37:28','2026-03-07 08:40:05',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(172,5,'outgoing','text','Hello!\n\nThank you for your interest in obtaining a Canada visa. At Parrot Canada, we specialize in helping clients like you secure study permits, work visas, and permanent residence for Canada with expert guidance throughout the entire process.\n\nHere’s how we can assist you:\n\n1. **Eligibility Assessment**: We start with a detailed evaluation of your profile to determine the best visa pathway for you.  \n2. **Application Preparation**: We help you gather the required documents, complete application forms, and prepare a strong submission.  \n3. **Submission & Follow-Up**: We ensure your application is submitted correctly and monitor its progress.  \n4. **Pay After Approval**: Our fees are only payable once your Canada visa is approved—no risk to you.  \n5. **Post-Arrival Support**: We provide settlement assistance to help you adapt smoothly after arriving in Canada.\n\nTo get started, please email us at **infos@visaconsultantcanada.com** with some details about your background, your purpose of travel (study, work, or permanent residence), and any questions you have. We will promptly connect you with one of our experienced consultants to guide you through your Canada visa process.\n\nLooking forward to helping you achieve your goal of moving to Canada!',NULL,NULL,NULL,'delivered',0,0,NULL,'2026-03-07 08:37:33','2026-03-07 08:39:34','\"{\\\"confidence\\\":0.65,\\\"source\\\":\\\"grounded_ai\\\"}\"','wamid.HBgMOTcxNTQyMTk0NTc2FQIAERgSODhGRjE1RDkwNEM0MjZCOEJEAA==',NULL,NULL),(173,4,'incoming','text','ishimwewilson24@gmail.com',NULL,NULL,NULL,'received',0,1,NULL,'2026-03-07 09:54:58','2026-03-07 09:55:05',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(174,4,'outgoing','text','✅ Thank you! You can now ask your questions.',NULL,NULL,NULL,'read',0,0,NULL,'2026-03-07 09:54:58','2026-03-07 15:41:59','\"{\\\"confidence\\\":1,\\\"source\\\":\\\"system_onboarding\\\"}\"','wamid.HBgMMjUwNzkyMzU5MDM0FQIAERgSQjBGRDUxQUE1QzRGNTg2NUZCAA==',NULL,NULL),(175,4,'incoming','text','You are most welcome',NULL,NULL,NULL,'received',0,1,NULL,'2026-03-07 15:42:27','2026-03-07 15:45:04',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(176,4,'outgoing','text','Thank you! How can I assist you with your visa application or related inquiries today?',NULL,NULL,NULL,'read',0,0,NULL,'2026-03-07 15:42:31','2026-03-07 15:42:36','\"{\\\"confidence\\\":0.5,\\\"source\\\":\\\"ai\\\"}\"','wamid.HBgMMjUwNzkyMzU5MDM0FQIAERgSQzBCMjMzMEVDMUJDRUVDMDE4AA==',NULL,NULL),(177,4,'incoming','text','I want VISA',NULL,NULL,NULL,'received',0,1,NULL,'2026-03-07 15:42:37','2026-03-07 15:45:04',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(178,4,'outgoing','text','Thank you for your interest in obtaining a visa! We are here to help you through every step of the application process. To get started, could you please let me know:\n\n1. The country you want to get a visa for.\n2. The type of visa you need (e.g., study, work, tourist, etc.).\n3. Any specific questions or concerns you have about the visa process.\n\nWe also provide comprehensive visa interview preparation, expert guidance aligned with the latest official requirements, and operate on a pay-after-approval fee model to minimize your financial risk.\n\nFeel free to share more details, and we\'ll make sure to support you fully!',NULL,NULL,NULL,'read',0,0,NULL,'2026-03-07 15:42:40','2026-03-07 15:42:43','\"{\\\"confidence\\\":0.65,\\\"source\\\":\\\"grounded_ai\\\"}\"','wamid.HBgMMjUwNzkyMzU5MDM0FQIAERgSQkY2QzFCNkEzOERCRTA0MjEwAA==',NULL,NULL),(179,4,'incoming','text','I want VISA for studying in Canada. I come from Rwanda. What is required to get it?',NULL,NULL,NULL,'received',0,1,NULL,'2026-03-07 16:25:09','2026-03-07 16:30:05',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(180,4,'outgoing','text','Thank you for reaching out! Since you are from Rwanda and want to study in Canada, here is a general overview of the requirements and steps to apply for a Canadian study permit (student visa):\n\n### Key Requirements for a Canadian Study Permit:\n1. **Letter of Acceptance:** You must have an acceptance letter from a Designated Learning Institution (DLI) in Canada.\n2. **Proof of Financial Support:** You need to show that you have enough money to pay for tuition fees, living expenses for yourself and any family members who come with you, and return transportation.\n3. **Identity Documents:** Valid passport and two recent passport-sized photos.\n4. **Letter of Explanation:** A letter that explains why you want to study in Canada and confirm that you understand your responsibilities as a student.\n5. **Proof of Ties to Your Home Country:** To demonstrate that you will leave Canada at the end of your studies.\n6. **Custodian Declaration (if under 18):** If you are a minor, this document might be required.\n7. **Biometrics:** You will likely have to provide fingerprints and photos.\n8. **Medical Exam:** In some cases, you may have to undergo a medical examination.\n9. **English or French Language Proficiency:** Depending on the institution\'s requirements.\n\n### Application Process Overview:\n1. Find and apply to a DLI in Canada.\n2. Obtain a Letter of Acceptance.\n3. Prepare your documentation as listed above.\n4. Apply online or at the Canadian visa application center.\n5. Provide biometrics and medical exam if requested.\n6. Wait for the assessment and decision.\n\n---\n\n### How Parrot Canada Visa Consultant Co. Ltd Can Help:\n- We have expertise in Canadian study permits and will guide you through:\n  - Selecting a suitable university or college.\n  - Preparing and reviewing your application to strengthen approval chances.\n  - Assisting with financial documentation.\n  - Explaining requirements specific to applicants from Rwanda.\n  - Helping with biometrics and medical exams.\n  - Providing post-approval settlement support.\n\n### Local Support in Rwanda:\nWe have offices in Kigali and Musanze, Rwanda, where you can get personalized assistance throughout the application process.\n\n---\n\n### Contact Us:\nYou can visit or contact our Rwanda offices for detailed guidance:\n- **Email:** infos@visaconsultantcanada.com  \n- **Phone:** +260 972 968 285 (Zambia office phone, Rwanda phone likely available on inquiry)  \n- **Locations:** Kigali and Musanze, Rwanda\n\n---\n\nIf you’d like, I can provide a checklist tailored to your situation or help you schedule a consultation with one of our expert advisors in Rwanda. Please let me know!',NULL,NULL,NULL,'read',0,0,NULL,'2026-03-07 16:25:21','2026-03-07 16:28:32','\"{\\\"confidence\\\":0.65,\\\"source\\\":\\\"grounded_ai\\\"}\"','wamid.HBgMMjUwNzkyMzU5MDM0FQIAERgSODQyQjQ1RDg3RjMwRUEwMUQ1AA==',NULL,NULL),(181,6,'incoming','text','Hello',NULL,NULL,NULL,'received',1,1,'2026-03-15 12:39:09','2026-03-07 16:36:34','2026-03-15 12:39:09',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(182,6,'outgoing','text','Welcome 👋\nBefore we continue, please provide your *full name*.',NULL,NULL,NULL,'delivered',0,0,NULL,'2026-03-07 16:36:34','2026-03-07 16:36:38','\"{\\\"confidence\\\":1,\\\"source\\\":\\\"system_onboarding\\\"}\"','wamid.HBgNODYxMzEzMjU3NzQ0MBUCABEYEkJBRjE2NEQ4OTU0MkI1Q0Y3MAA=',NULL,NULL),(183,6,'incoming','text','IKUZWE YVONE Bienvenue',NULL,NULL,NULL,'received',1,1,'2026-03-15 12:39:09','2026-03-07 16:36:47','2026-03-15 12:3