26-03-14 06:34:20','2026-03-14 06:32:49','2026-03-14 06:34:20',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(725,22,'outgoing','text','For studying a Master\'s in the United States through our consultancy, you can choose between two packages:\n\n1. Loan-Based Program:\n- Registration & Application Fee: USD 150\n- Loan Approval Stage: USD 1,200\n- Mock Interview Preparation: USD 150\n- After Visa Approval: USD 1,500\n- Total Package: USD 3,000\n\n2. Without Loan:\n- Registration & Application Fee: USD 150\n- Mock Interview Preparation: USD 150\n- After Visa Approval: USD 2,000\n- Total Package: USD 2,300\n\nThe registration fee is refundable if admission is not secured within four months.\n\nLet us know if you want to start your application or need further assistance!',NULL,NULL,NULL,'read',0,0,NULL,'2026-03-14 06:32:53','2026-03-14 06:32:56','\"{\\\"confidence\\\":0.65,\\\"source\\\":\\\"grounded_ai\\\"}\"','wamid.HBgMMjUwNzg1NTY5MTQxFQIAERgSRUM2OUI3NzI4NjZDRjU4REVGAA==',NULL,NULL),(733,23,'incoming','text','HEY',NULL,NULL,NULL,'received',0,1,NULL,'2026-03-15 04:41:31','2026-03-15 04:45:04',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(734,23,'outgoing','text','Welcome 👋\nBefore we continue, please provide your *full name*.',NULL,NULL,NULL,'sent',0,0,NULL,'2026-03-15 04:41:31','2026-03-15 04:41:34','\"{\\\"confidence\\\":1,\\\"source\\\":\\\"system_onboarding\\\"}\"','wamid.HBgLMTQzODI5MDY2ODgVAgARGBIyMjY5NkIzRkRBNzBDREZENDQA',NULL,NULL),(735,23,'incoming','text','DR JEAN PIERRE TWAJAMAHORO',NULL,NULL,NULL,'received',0,1,NULL,'2026-03-15 04:41:46','2026-03-15 04:45:04',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(736,23,'outgoing','text','Thank you DR JEAN PIERRE TWAJAMAHORO 😊\nNow please provide your *email address*.',NULL,NULL,NULL,'read',0,0,NULL,'2026-03-15 04:41:46','2026-03-15 04:42:16','\"{\\\"confidence\\\":1,\\\"source\\\":\\\"system_onboarding\\\"}\"','wamid.HBgLMTQzODI5MDY2ODgVAgARGBI2RkQ4NjVGMzVEMDg1OEI5MTEA',NULL,NULL),(737,23,'incoming','text','twajeepeter@gmail.com',NULL,NULL,NULL,'received',0,1,NULL,'2026-03-15 04:42:13','2026-03-15 04:45:04',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(738,23,'outgoing','text','✅ Thank you! You can now ask your questions.',NULL,NULL,NULL,'read',0,0,NULL,'2026-03-15 04:42:13','2026-03-15 04:45:39','\"{\\\"confidence\\\":1,\\\"source\\\":\\\"system_onboarding\\\"}\"','wamid.HBgLMTQzODI5MDY2ODgVAgARGBIxNUQ3ODYzNDE0QkI1OTExODYA',NULL,NULL),(739,23,'incoming','text','which service do you provide?',NULL,NULL,NULL,'received',0,1,NULL,'2026-03-15 04:42:32','2026-03-15 04:45:04',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(740,23,'outgoing','text','Parrot Canada Visa Consultant Co. Ltd provides comprehensive education and visa consultancy services to support students and professionals who want to study or travel abroad. This includes helping with school and program selection, securing Letters of Acceptance (LOA) from partner universities, preparing financial documents for visa applications, obtaining necessary documents like Form I-20 for the USA and Provincial Attestation Letter (PAL) for Canada, and assisting with visa applications through licensed immigration partners. Additional services include scholarship guidance, university admission support, Permanent Residence (PR) applications, and job-seeking assistance for graduates and professionals.',NULL,NULL,NULL,'read',0,0,NULL,'2026-03-15 04:42:36','2026-03-15 04:45:39','\"{\\\"confidence\\\":0.65,\\\"source\\\":\\\"grounded_ai\\\"}\"','wamid.HBgLMTQzODI5MDY2ODgVAgARGBI5QTg0QUZERkFCODYxQTM4RTEA',NULL,NULL),(741,23,'incoming','text','which countries?',NULL,NULL,NULL,'received',0,1,NULL,'2026-03-15 04:44:27','2026-03-15 04:45:04',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(742,23,'outgoing','text','You can apply to universities and visa programs in Canada, the United States, Germany, France, Turkey, North Cyprus, Italy, Hungary, Lithuania, Netherlands, Ireland, Malta, Russia, Belarus, Romania, Albania, South Korea, Malaysia, China, India, and many other countries worldwide through Parrot Canada Visa Consultant.',NULL,NULL,NULL,'read',0,0,NULL,'2026-03-15 04:44:30','2026-03-15 04:45:39','\"{\\\"confidence\\\":0.65,\\\"source\\\":\\\"grounded_ai\\\"}\"','wamid.HBgLMTQzODI5MDY2ODgVAgARGBJENDdEMDMxQkFBOUExNkI4MTQA',NULL,NULL),(743,23,'incoming','text','which type of visa?',NULL,NULL,NULL,'received',0,1,NULL,'2026-03-15 04:45:15','2026-03-15 04:50:05',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(744,23,'outgoing','text','Parrot Canada Visa Consultant primarily assists with study visas, helping students with admission and visa applications. They also provide support for visitor visas, business visas, work visas, and Canadian Permanent Residence (PR) applications through their licensed immigration partner. If you need assistance with any of these visa types, their team can guide you through the process.',NULL,NULL,NULL,'read',0,0,NULL,'2026-03-15 04:45:17','2026-03-15 04:50:38','\"{\\\"confidence\\\":0.65,\\\"source\\\":\\\"grounded_ai\\\"}\"','wamid.HBgLMTQzODI5MDY2ODgVAgARGBI5MzBCMzU4RTlFREVFQkE3MDgA',NULL,NULL),(745,23,'incoming','text','GREAT WHAT ABOUT SCHOLARSHIP?',NULL,NULL,NULL,'received',0,1,NULL,'2026-03-15 04:51:06','2026-03-15 04:55:05',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(746,23,'outgoing','text','Yes, Parrot Canada Visa Consultant provides scholarship guidance and financial aid support to help students reduce study abroad costs. They assist in identifying suitable scholarships, preparing documents, and applying through partner universities and scholarship platforms. Scholarships typically range from partial tuition discounts (10% to 90%) mainly in Canada, the USA, and Europe, with some countries like North Cyprus and Turkey offering high-percentage scholarships. Full scholarships are mostly available in China for Master’s and PhD programs.',NULL,NULL,NULL,'read',0,0,NULL,'2026-03-15 04:51:08','2026-03-15 04:58:26','\"{\\\"confidence\\\":0.65,\\\"source\\\":\\\"grounded_ai\\\"}\"','wamid.HBgLMTQzODI5MDY2ODgVAgARGBJFRDA4OTMzOEU4QzMyMENDRkYA',NULL,NULL),(908,14,'incoming','text','Hey',NULL,NULL,NULL,'received',0,1,NULL,'2026-03-15 16:09:23','2026-03-15 16:10:05',NUL