red for visa applications\r\n•	Obtaining the Form I-20 for USA student visas\r\n•	Obtaining the Provincial Attestation Letter (PAL) for Canada study permits\r\n•	Visa application assistance through licensed immigration expert partners, including trusted professionals such as BorderPass in Canada\r\n•	Assistance with Permanent Residence (PR) applications through our partner BorderPass (this is an additional service and not our main mission)\r\n•	Assistance in job seeking opportunities for graduates and professionals (this is an additional support service and not our primary mission)\r\nFrom the initial consultation to the final visa decision, Parrot Canada Visa Consultant Co. Ltd ensures that students receive professional guidance to successfully begin their international education and move abroad journey.',NULL,NULL,NULL,'read',0,0,NULL,'2026-03-15 16:10:19','2026-03-15 16:10:22','\"{\\\"confidence\\\":0.95,\\\"source\\\":\\\"keyword_match\\\"}\"','wamid.HBgMMjU0NzExODA3NjQ2FQIAERgSOEExRkJBNDIwNzRCMDAyMUQ0AA==',NULL,NULL),(916,14,'incoming','text','Where is the company office ?',NULL,NULL,NULL,'received',0,1,NULL,'2026-03-15 16:11:17','2026-03-15 16:15:05',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(917,14,'outgoing','text','The headquarter is located Canada in Quebec Province and Montreal city while main office in Africa is located in Kigali, Rwanda, with partner offices and representatives in countries such as Kenya, Ghana, Zambia, Tanzania, South Korea, and others.\r\nMore information visit: https://visaconsultantcanada.com/Contact_us',NULL,NULL,NULL,'delivered',0,0,NULL,'2026-03-15 16:11:17','2026-03-15 16:11:21','\"{\\\"confidence\\\":0.95,\\\"source\\\":\\\"keyword_match\\\"}\"','wamid.HBgMMjU0NzExODA3NjQ2FQIAERgSMTMzRDQ2Q0Q2QUE1NjAyMjgyAA==',NULL,NULL),(918,14,'outgoing','text','[Attachment]',NULL,NULL,NULL,'delivered',0,0,NULL,'2026-03-15 16:11:17','2026-03-15 16:11:20','\"{\\\"type\\\":\\\"image\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https:\\\\\\/\\\\\\/parrotcanada.site\\\\\\/storage\\\\\\/faq_at